Reqs
- A resource (file) can be attached to one or multiple tags.
- For a given tag, list all the resource
- For a given resource, get all the tags
- Identify the top tags
- Trending tags (We can use LRU cache strategy)
- Recommend tag


Soln

Entity
-------
Tag
- name
- _id

Resource
- type
- name
- _id
- List<Tag_id>

Repo
Map<_id, Tag> tags
Map<_id, Resource> resources
Map<tag_id, List<resource_id>>
Heap<tag_id, count>


View
- List<Resource> search(tag_id)
- List<Tag> search(resource_id)
- List<Tag> topTags()

